claim.claim-text:
A tire vulcanizer comprising:
the unloading device according to any one of claims 1 to 6;
a vulcanizer main body which performs vulcanization on a green tire which is not vulcanized;
a post-cure inflator which cools the vulcanized tire vulcanized by the vulcanizer main body, at the cooling position; and
an exporting device for discharging the vulcanized tire cooled at the cooling position.
